{"tid":1659734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫過岑子杰簽支持同意書既人注意個人安全","createTime":"2019-10-17T06:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T09:07:01.000Z","uid":34472,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d82373a4b39cde83e10fb6bc23d08ad17c30c9c","tid":1659734,"uid":34472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的 有朋友係做議員助理<br />\n今日去去沙田民政署做嘢既時候聽到其他候選人話<br />\n曾經有一隊popo去過沙田區議會office<br />\n咁大家都知岺子杰會參選沙田瀝源<br />\n唔排除popo係會攞咗候選人提名名單<br />\n所以要留意個人安全<br />\n當然唔止提名人 亦包括各位手足<br />\n全民運動 強身健體<br />\n咪掛住睇 出手救人啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b204872060eac8b456b1990d7203f3dce6433551","tid":1659734,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b55287db3bf681a09e0c9c9cc50f949eae515407","tid":1659734,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eb31904b9c9c5ab3e75ff0521499c27819fdb897","tid":1659734,"uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"出街要多留意四周環境, 唔好掛住睇 MON 行路"}]}